{"tid":782810,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［慢性蕁痲疹］無解致敏源 醫生都話無得醫","createTime":"2018-08-17T05:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:44:24.000Z","uid":201220,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"bda19aaca694bdb156e57c8df22f4b640ab29346","tid":782810,"uid":201220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"之前以為敏感離自己好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但半年前開始 日日皮膚都會過敏<br />\n睇完皮膚科醫生話係慢性蕁痲疹 仲話無得醫 都唔知係咩原因引起 可以空氣 壓力等等 仲話只可以等佢自己退 所以得開左d抗組織胺紓緩過敏既痕癢<br />\n但成日食抗組織胺搞到個人又虛又好支力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人可以分享下 有咩分法可以改善甚至斷尾？"},{"pid":"5c347cf2556818563a29a92ad74217edb7b656ae","tid":782810,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:20:31.000Z","msg":"殺咗肥大細胞"},{"pid":"79332054b009dc43157e2fd0b4acf769b701e91c","tid":782810,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:21:36.000Z","msg":"呢條友又係你咁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fat,_Sick_and_Nearly_Dead\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFat%2C_Sick_and_Nearly_Dead&d=0ME6ik%2BdFVAdTzaqX0vXmRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ca7206d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fat,_Sick_and_Nearly_Dead</a>"},{"pid":"573019b23d94baf087d02afbeb4af1d76c3bd6c6","tid":782810,"uid":201220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79332054b009dc43157e2fd0b4acf769b701e91c","tid":782810,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:21:36.000Z","msg":"呢條友又係你咁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fat,_Sick_and_Nearly_Dead\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFat%2C_Sick_and_Nearly_Dead&d=0ME6ik%2BdFVAdTzaqX0vXmRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ca7206d9\" data-auto-link targe