TEN TABLETS 20MG works for me, hope it helps you</blockquote>"},{"pid":"eb9faee4d8d42bee0d7b2fdf13ed42e1a8962eab","tid":782810,"uid":45487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:40:58.000Z","msg":"我都有呀<br />\n不過唔痕同埋R佢就越生越多<br />\n但唔理佢一陣又會好返<br />\n冇諗住睇醫生因為自己情況唔算嚴重 未影響到生活<br />\n我都諗住學上面位巴打咁 用運動黎解決個問題<br />\n始終皮膚病搵唔到個致敏源 又點醫呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上果啲抗組織胺 我上網睇過話有副作用 就放棄左<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fd81d6ddabd32255da59ea6e6526ee143c7343","tid":782810,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"same <br />\n而家要keep 住食敏感藥先無事<br />\n一過鐘唔食就會起<br />\n唔知我死先定個肝死先"},{"pid":"0fbdfc85c0a43dfddb406393fa9556d9d83c383b","tid":782810,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a47298a5688378697de1721a5333b2015a3e80f1","tid":782810,"uid":135211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72c9ab4047c24dfe76a21b8b98bf8d17fc4d764b","tid":782810,"uid":140580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db9fe428796e82e3802767ef91d5fbf68d463ec9","tid":782810,"uid":140580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"醫生開 <br />\n你可以試下"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:40:54.000Z","msg":"因為我都出得好勁下<br />\n壓到刮到又會出<br />\n唔掂都會忽然出好大撻 講緊可能係成條頸都一大片<br />\n或者個身勁多粒<br />\n連嘴唇 眼皮都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以可能咁醫生就開類固醇俾我<br />\n但真係有用<br />\n出咗半年食中藥都冇斷尾<br />\n類固醇食咗一排就停咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:43:31.000Z","msg":"多謝強國送大禮<br />\n<br />\n去外國一轉 包你舒服番"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:42:58.000Z","msg":"無用, 去到外國空氣清新一樣會起"},{"pid":"e83365649af57efb506612b6d7904d6431872a0f","tid":782810,"uid":201220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"055d6f9e6f1632100ee5a9d1fc2218273b60f446","tid":782810,"uid":194015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"